OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJD Sports accused of       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'irresponsible' motorbike  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fad                         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, JD Sports has come under fire for      
OL,6, posting an advert showing motorcyclists
OL,7, wearing trainers - footwear deemed     
OL,8, unsuitable for riding a motorbike.     
OL,10,FThe advertising watchdog has received  
OL,11,Fmore than 40 complaints about the ad   
OL,12,Ffor Nike Air Max 95s, which also       
OL,13,Ffeatures stunts such as wheelies.      
OL,15,FMotorcycle groups criticised JD Sports 
OL,16,Ffor promoting "inappropriate" footwear 
OL,17,Fand "irresponsible" riding.            
OL,19,FThe company defended its ad and said it
OL,20,Ftakes health and safety very seriously.
